         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">25, WILTON PLACE. S.W. ¶ Decr 25 /71 ¶ My dear Sir ¶  ¶ I can now at last report that I am fairly at work at the sixth vol. of Flora Australiensis ¶  and if health and strength admit hope to go on ste...</supplied>
            </head>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.12.25</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M3, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">25, WILTON PLACE. S.W.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Decr 25 /71</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I can now at last report that I am fairly at work at the sixth vol. of Flora Australiensis<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Bentham (1863-78).</p>
               </note> and if health and strength admit hope to go on steadily till I get through it. I have begun with <name key="Pimelea">Pimelea</name> in which the sections must in many respects be different from those of Meissner<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Meisner (1857a), </seg>pp. 496-518<seg style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> which separate widely closely allied and in some cases identical species.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Many thanks for the pains you have taken to get the £100 transmitted<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Victorian Government</seg>
                     <seg style="">'</seg>
                     <seg style="">s contribution for Bentham (1863-78), vol. 6.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> — I shall shortly apply to Mr Verdon for it — but as it is usually transmitted in bills having some time to run it will not be due yet — nor do I feel entitled to it till I have advanced the work a little further.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have finished the <name key="Compositae">Compositae</name> for Genera Plantarum<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham &amp; Hooker (1862-83), vol. 2, part 1, pp. 163-533.</p>
               </note> all but a few references here and there and all is written out for Press we are now only waiting for Hookers <name key="Rubiaceae">Rubiaceae</name>
               <note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham &amp; Hooker (1862-83), vol. 2, part 1, pp. 7-151.</p>
               </note> which are very nearly ready and we hope to go to press next month. I adopt about 750 genera of <name key="Compositae">Compositae</name> with about 1400 synonyms — Hooker has I believe about 300 genera of <name key="Rubiaceae">Rubiaceae</name>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If I do not write by next mail it will mean that I am going on regularly with the volume without anything having occurred requiring special notice. I have quite given up all unnecessary correspondence.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>George Bentham</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Ferd v. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
